&lt;li&gt;10+ years of software engineering experience, including senior technical leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of owning large, ambiguous systems in production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of system design, failure modes, and operational excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong intuition for AI agent behavior, evaluation, and risk management&lt;/li&gt;
